</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Purse printhead 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Execute SDS 07-6-002 using "Filling pulse" 3 times 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Check air hoses and manifolds for possible blockades which causes failing PH-vacuum 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Presence of 250012 "Unexpected ink drop" might indicate on blockade. 
